# Contract lockdown

- Protected: `packages/contracts/src/`
- Only LSA authorizes contract edits
- Each change needs impact summary + breaking/non-breaking label
- Update `packages/contracts/src/contracts.spec.ts` when routes or DTOs change
- Implementation in apps must consume contracts — never redefine shapes locally
